<h5 class="proof">
<span class="type">Proof of Theorem</span> <span class="acro">RPNC</span>
</h5>
<p>Let $r$ be the number of nonzero rows in a row-equivalent matrix in reduced row-echelon form.
By <a class="knowl" acro="CRN" type="Theorem" title="Computing Rank and Nullity" knowl="./knowls/theorem.CRN.knowl">Theorem CRN</a>,
\begin{equation*}
\rank{A}+\nullity{A}= r+(n-r)=n
\end{equation*}</p>

